# Simple geometry for a cube that centers around the origin. Made 4 vertices for each face (many are identical)
#####################
#Front face
v -1.0 -1.0 1.0
v 1.0 -1.0 1.0
v 1.0 1.0 1.0
v -1.0 1.0 1.0

#Back face
v -1.0 -1.0 -1.0
v -1.0 1.0 -1.0
v 1.0 1.0 -1.0
v 1.0 -1.0 -1.0

#Top face
v -1.0 1.0 -1.0
v -1.0 1.0 1.0
v 1.0 1.0 1.0
v 1.0 1.0 -1.0

#Bottom face
v -1.0 -1.0 -1.0
v 1.0 -1.0 -1.0
v 1.0 -1.0 1.0
v -1.0 -1.0 1.0

#Right face
v 1.0 -1.0 -1.0
v 1.0 1.0 -1.0
v 1.0 1.0 1.0
v 1.0 -1.0 1.0

#Left face
v -1.0 -1.0 -1.0
v -1.0 -1.0 1.0
v -1.0 1.0 1.0
v -1.0 1.0 -1.0
